# 🛡️ CySA+ Hands-On Lab Journal

Welcome! This repository documents my hands-on cybersecurity practice while completing **CompTIA CySA+ labs**.  
It showcases my ability to work with industry tools, investigate threats, analyze vulnerabilities, and document findings in a professional format.  

---

## 👨‍💻 About Me
I’m **Eric Johnson**, a cybersecurity professional with CompTIA Security+ and CySA+ certifications.  
I enjoy working with vulnerability management, SOC operations, and threat analysis.  
This repo highlights how I approach problems, use security tools, and reflect on real-world applications.  

- 📫 [LinkedIn](https://linkedin.com/in/eric-johnson-6351a919b)  
- 💻 [GitHub Portfolio](https://github.com/ericjohnson4)

